**+FIX: ADDED TERRORIST SPEED X2, please re-download!**

**As promised the final version of trap challenge death run map! All bugs fixed and trap sounds added. Still includes the bunny hop, knife and easy stages. Enjoy!**

**Includes: 20-Traps, 30-CT spawns, 2-T spawns, 4-Secrets**

**At the finish of the map, you can choose:** 

**-bunny hopping**

**-knife arena**

**-easy (gun & terrorist)**

**For any mistakes please do not flag the map, it would be nicer if you comment and I will fix the problem.**

> **Install the map by simply overwriting the old cstrike folder with the new one in the download.**

**As always commenting and rating is welcome :D**
